description:
@HACK 2025 is the 2nd edition of @HACK - a Canadian Capture The Flag (CTF) competition, hosted by HEXPLOIT ALLIANCE and TECHNATION at Concordia University in Montreal.

Dates: March 1st-2nd, 2025

Challenges: https://github.com/athack-ctf/AtHackCTF-2025-Challenges

@HACK is Canada’s top annual student CTF (Capture the Flag) cybersecurity competition, run by TECHNATION and Hexploit Alliance.

P.S. We occasionally use the term “cybersecurity hackathon” to make things clearer for newcomers, though the event is still a true CTF.

Location: Concordia University’s downtown Montréal campus, Quebec, Canada.
